nce of new hierarchy levels and that it is the\nabsolute amount of information, not relative, which governs such behavior.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Nov 2013 17:11:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 Jun 2014 21:15:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
