he\ntransport in the system is much lower than the carrier density, in accord with\nthe theoretical model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Nov 2013 21:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Sep 2014 14:01:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-01"}
